title: 11YA: Four Famed Females
body_text:
Members of the ECD nation are still buzzing about the massive 11YA main attraction featuring Lauren Stopa, Melissa Kerr, Alison Bertsch, and Diana DiBuccio.
These four titans have withstood the onslaught of weapons launched primarily by their male counterparts, yet remain the only true championship-winning women in the game. Simply put, they are the greatest.
Below is a fraction of their enviable lists of accomplishments. Cheers, ladies - see you on August 27!
